text: KRAY-FM (103.5 FM) is a radio station broadcasting a Regional Mexican format. Licensed to Salinas, California, United States, it serves the Santa Cruz area. The station is currently owned by Wolfhouse Radio Group, Inc.. ==External links== * RAY-FM Category:Radio stations established in 1966 RAY-FM Category:1966 establishments in California Category:Santa Cruz, California
